MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Shift loop: setup -> 3-minute shift -> graded report card (S/A/B/C) with
  localStorage best score
- Order profiles (Beverage / High-Mix E-comm / Pharma-Glass) feed the REAL
  optimizer; constraint toggles (heavy_low, fragile_high, max_height 1200/1500)
  re-plan the next pattern live and can be re-queued mid-shift
- Speed override 50/75/100/150% maps to URScript v-scaling; >100% triples
  organic misfeed probability, scaled further by box fragility — the cell now
  misbehaves on its own, sabotage deck kept for deterministic testing
- Held-frame decision: below-gate frames pause motion and offer an operator
  override with a real 30% rework risk (-15 pts) — teaching exactly why the
  shipped engine never writes under 0.95 autonomously
- Point economy (+5 placement, profile pallet bonus, +10 gate-passed
  correction, -20 latched E-stop), live throughput/min, shift countdown
- Fixes: telemetry timestamps now monotonic across pallets, footer card
  layout, ProgressMeter hardcoded n/6 -> n/MISSIONS.length

Verified: next build clean; node game-loop test — constraints honored by
optimizer (620mm under 1200 cap), 10 organic slips/60s at 150% pharma,
override rework path, mid-shift re-plan under cloud outage from cache
